{"tid":1526851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"機場唔夠人呀 唔該開post 傳出去","createTime":"2019-09-01T07:47:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T09:31:37.000Z","uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0cd0d9ae9f8e807088c972bec36341c58198d813","tid":1526851,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:47:31.000Z","msg":"我係呂麗乳搖巴！！！！<br />\n連登唔夠機場Post啊啊啊啊啊！！！！<br />\n大家快D自行Copy下面段野去開Post覆Post<br />\n<br />\n901 機場攻略<br />\n麻煩大家用盡所有方法傳開佢<br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: red;\">準時</span>到機場，唔係一點先出門口<br />\n- 衣着同裝備冇任何限制，最緊要保護自己<br />\n- 集合地點：機場巴士總站(暢達路)<br />\n- 測試方法：排隊戰術，見到<span style=\"color: red;\">有隊就排</span>；利用人數優勢，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好單獨行事</span><br />\n- 唔好同任何遊客有肢體碰撞<br />\n- 去機場：<span style=\"color: red;\">以巴士為優先</span>，機場快線集中係香港同青衣站上車<br />\n- 已經準備左幾套應變方案，根據現場情況<span style=\"color: red;\">隨時轉變</span>，要密切留意住 901 機場 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=dE5eED8%2BMjLqHtNzOSR2X20Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=8006434c\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5XusdO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5XusdO.jpg&h=31adcd48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cTXKf68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcTXKf68.jpg&h=74d57433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qAxaV7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqAxaV7a.jpg&h=13c2eb06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/otZAnNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FotZAnNa.jpg&h=f10fa124&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cf9c23c52425ed75c94c30ca890a04c6a5319d23","tid":1526851,"uid":1945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:48:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hO54gA1.jpg\" data-thumbn